:29:31.000Z","msg":"仲要high同depress都冇原因冇先兆<br />\n突然間全世界所有野都好負面，自己個腦不斷咁樣講<br />\n嚴重既連身體都會有反應<br />\n<br />\n因為冇原因地發作，所以係冇方向點樣解決"},{"pid":"435d6e2bb67788faa15e918cfa5009c9cdff8af4","tid":768043,"uid":10482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0aac8dace3beef728c898119599ef8228a26364c","tid":768043,"uid":31208,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"d65bed10e0e9fc9e6ba294fcdd69de83bff543a1","tid":768043,"uid":22349,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"小肥昨日（4日）與Ellen為ViuTV節目《全民造星》錄影，對於Ellen墮斃，悲痛莫名的小肥在社交平台出post：「我復原能力再快，都接受唔到接二連三嘅打擊，我真係頂唔到&hellip;&hellip;」另他以短訊回覆東網，指昨日錄影時不發覺Ellen有任何異樣，二人有傾偈，現在他深感悲痛，更透露：「今朝八點Ellen仲有Whatsapp我，約聽晚飲嘢。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"今朝仲約人聽晚飲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"卓韻芝都有喺ig講同rockmui約咗飲野"},{"pid":"ddae1aeb2d086adf05c75ed480202ad0f8655781","tid":768043,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af60e1e988eb569a805b3351513beab6476adf42","tid":768043,"uid":7323,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"陳淨心最大嫌疑"},{"pid":"d51bbb375f4b7bf89f994e6c0617e2215d06d68a","tid":768043,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af60e1e988eb569a805b3351513beab6476adf42","tid":768043,"uid":7323,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"陳淨心最大嫌疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"直頭啦"},{"pid":"61f75801f928b1551e99d4137970a49cd03c4d1f","tid":768043,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"老狗認同"},{"pid":"4fb451a35df123bf1ca86abea1fcda2a08e5e31e","tid":768043,"uid":294,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"5分鐘仲約緊人<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘後就跳樓<br />\